# Production config is now resolved at runtime from Dataverse Environment Variables
# via resolveRuntimeConfig() in @spaarke/auth.
#
# The following values are no longer needed at build time:
#   VITE_BFF_BASE_URL  -> resolved from sprk_BffApiBaseUrl env var
#   VITE_MSAL_CLIENT_ID -> resolved from sprk_MsalClientId env var
